{"tid":1702131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以後狗發言睇清楚D，分分有線索","createTime":"2019-11-09T14:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T03:46:07.000Z","uid":295813,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4e5050ac84abab43eafa6063882c2db91132729b","tid":1702131,"uid":295813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"今日<br />\n網上有傳一名女子被捕後遭警方性侵，其後要到伊利沙伯醫院接受墮胎手術。警方回應查詢時表示，投訴警察課上月22日收到一名律師代表報案，指他的當事人聲稱於9月27日，於荃灣警署內被強姦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家係咪有印象之前狗話無性侵呢。</span><br />\n<br />\n再睇下呢段:<br />\n於「反修例運動」中，警方多次使用<strong>新屋嶺拘留中心</strong>羈留被捕人士，多次傳出被捕者在中心被虐待、甚至被性侵犯的消息。保安局局長李家超今日（6日）到立法會接受口頭質詢，重申至今沒有收到<strong>有關性侵犯</strong>的投訴，但在立法會議員朱凱迪追問下卻透露，新屋嶺一直沒有安裝閉路電視，直至今年十月才安裝。<br />\n<br />\n佢地答野好捉字蝨，但同時亦都證明左係某D問題到，如果佢地答得<span style=\"color: red;\">好指定地點/時間/人物/動作</span>果陣，即係件事係<span style=\"color: red;\">真</span>，但有部分資訊出錯先唔認。<br />\n<br />\n例子(如有雷同，實屬巧合):<br />\n警方:當晚無防暴警察同便衣狗進入現場。<br />\n事實:當晚有休班狗進入現場。<br />\n<br />\n手足，沉冤待雪。<br />\n真相只有一個。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491016-20191109.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491016-20191109.htm&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSptqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=a9a293e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1491016-20191109.htm&h=8dac8bbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1491016-20191109.htm</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%8B%E5%B6%BA%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4-%E5%8D%81%E6%9C%88%E6%89%8D%E8%A3%9D%E9%96%89%E8%B7%AF%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25B6%25BA%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E5%258D%2581%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2589%258D%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%2596%2589%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%2F&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSptqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=634f0755\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25B6%25BA%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E5%258D%2581%25E6%259C%2588%25E6%2589%258D%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%2596%2589%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A6%2596%2F&h=1c31a870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%8B%E5%B6%BA%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4-%E5%8D%81%E6%9C%88%E6%89%8D%E8%A3%9D%E9%96%89%E8%B7%AF%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96/</a>"},{"pid":"0968affcb4d1c7ad198542743e0966a8c48d1e35","tid":1702131,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"［預言］涉強姦警員會孭起整隊警隊罪行，並可能全家被滅口<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1701986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1701986</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3e7012c6e5a93aa92548e5d2fc338064db86db27","tid":1702131,"uid":213665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"口罩tg: asdzxc12359"},{"pid":"86613f70e783b50056c5086d310d68e9906ee84c","tid":1702131,"uid":147292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e7012c6e5a93aa92548e5d2fc338064db86db27","tid":1702131,"uid":213665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"口罩tg: asdzxc12359"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:46:07.000Z","msg":"pmed"}]}